UID:F6qVX_kE2nPkw4JNt_NNz
SUMMARY:Small Business Meetup
DTSTAMP:20260403T051037Z
DTSTART:20260415T230000Z
DESCRIPTION:Are you a small business owner \\(1-5 employees\\) who has been
	 in business less than 5 years? Would you like to meet with other small bu
	sinesses\, talk about best practices\, share business wisdom\, and build c
	ommunity? Please join fellow Cloud Room members in creating a small busine
